@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : getTotalNetworkDistance()
activate System

note right of System: The system calculates the total distance\ncovered by all active routes in the network.

System --> ATCC : returns total distance (km) and number of active routes
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml
